# Explicitly mark packaged / brand binaries as binary so Git never applies
# line-ending conversion, diff-as-text, or merge drivers to them. Git detects
# most of these via content sniffing already, but being explicit prevents
# accidents when contributors set core.autocrlf=true on Windows.
build/icon.ico binary
build/icon.icns binary
build/icon.png binary
build/*.bmp binary
build/*.jpg binary
build/*.jpeg binary
